Text.string: Vault Hunter! Over here!
We need to find Talon before Mordecai notices she's gone!
Brick... do we really need FIFTY of these shock crystals?
Well, you get a lot of 'em at a time, so it ain't so bad!
What are you doing over there?
Oh, uh... j-just talking to myself. You know how I do! Keep looking!
Dammit! Someone take down that freakin' bird already!
Just keep following the trail, Vault Hunter.
Did we get it?! UGH! We STILL didn't get it?! Damn that bird!
Brick, dead end.
Found a dead end, Brick.
Looks like a dead end, Brick.
Dead end from the looks of it, Brick.
Come on, it's a MINE! There's gotta be some explosives you can use!
Okay, I got all the stupid shock crystals. Who needed these again?
Keep this under your codpiece, okay? I think Talon's gone missing. Vaughn said he saw some COV chasing a bird through the mines. Go track her down while I keep Mordecai busy.
Oh, uh. They're for some bounty board dude. Brrrrrendon! But like, with an “o”. Yeah. Yeah, yeah! Yeah.
Okay. What's really going on, Brick?
Nothing! Crystals. Nothing. Shut up! Leave me alone!
That should be enough. Time to load up the cart.
That should do the trick. Time to load up the cart.
This should be sufficient. Time to load up the cart.
That'll do 'er. Time to load up the cart.
Annnd, just a little push...
Guess I'll give it a push.
A push should do it.
Give 'er a little pushy-push, Zane-boy.
Talon located! In pursuit!
Talon's okay, Brick! I'm on her tail!
Talon is a survivor. I am tracking her now.
Found your girl Talon! Leggin' it after her!
Oh, man, that's a relief. I gotta keep Mordy busy, but you keep after her!
Huh? Keep after who now? I already wasted all these bandits, AND collected all these rifle parts.
Oh, uh, I mean, uh, the metaphorical her. The mission. Keep after her, man! The mission, yeah.
O-kaaay... will do, buddy. Will do.
Mordecai already lost one bird. My dude can't lose another one! His heart'll break! He's real sensitive, ya know.
No! Bad birdy! Go 'way!
Don't lose her! Mordy's gettin' suspicious.
Okay, I fetched all these boxes of cigars for some reason.
Good work, Mordy! We're doing important work out here!
Wait, were you just talkin' to someone?
No! You were!
I mean, I guess I was talkin' to you.
Thanks for proving my point! Now let's finish up this mission!
Talon's back.
Your girl has returned.
Talon returns.
Talon's headin' home to roost.
Damn, that's good to hear! Talon's comin' home!
You at the mine yet? We gotta find Talon. Let me know if you find something.
What was that?
Oh, I said... Fallon's... coming shmome.
You're being weird, Brick.
No I'm n—you are!
Talon flew right past us, and Mordecai followed her. Let's go!
You're a good momma, Talon. And I'm a proud uncle Mordecai.
Wait-wait-wait-wait-wait... you knew she was gone the whole time?
Yeah, man. She's been going off by herself and setting up this nest for a while now. Looks like the Vault Hunter helped her feed baby Redclaw, too.||—Hey, thanks for that.
Heh, heh. I think Talon says thanks, too.
Good work, Vault Hunter. Can you believe we got ourselves a baby Talon?! Little Redclaw is so damn cute! Eh, uh, stop. I'm getting all sensitive and shit. Damn!
Brick, looks like Talon's been busy. Cool bird.
Hey, Brick? Uh, looks like Talon can handle herself.
Brick, this Talon is quite the fearsome hunter.
Well, slap my tum and call me Holly—that bird is doing WORK, Brick.

Yeah, man. She's been going off by herself and settin' up this nest for a while now. Looks like the Vault Hunter helped her get ready to feed the baby with that juicy brain.||—And hey, thanks for that.
Looks like Brick had us both runnin' all over the place today, huh? But it's all good, 'cause the baby will have some food when he finally hatches. Thanks for lookin' after my girl.
I know she's tough, but I'm worried Talon's gettin' in over her head. Just follow the trail of... y'know, guts 'n' things. Seriously, Mordy would lose his mind if anything happened to Talon.
Are these... claw marks? Looks like Talon's been havin' fun.
Are these claw marks from Talon?
It would appear Mordecai's bird beast, Talon, is on the hunt.
Looks like Talon's havin' a guts party.
Hey, Vault Hunter. Vaughn just contacted me, said he saw some COV chasing a bird through the mines. It must have been Talon. Go track her down while I keep Mordecai busy.
Mordecai already lost one bird. My dude can't lose another one! His heart'll break! He's real sensitive, ya know.
